## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **AOC 1001 / del-desiran (Avidity Biosciences) Phase 2/3** = first FDA-trajectory DM1 ASO + antibody-oligonucleotide conjugate. transferrin receptor 1 (TfR1) antibody + DMPK CUG repeat-targeted ASO conjugate. 양자-VQE 의 RNA-oligonucleotide hairpin 결합 + antibody linker geometry.
2. **DYNE-101 (Dyne Therapeutics) Phase 2/3** = DM1 ASO with FORCE platform — Fab-based muscle-targeted oligonucleotide delivery. AOC 1001 와 mechanism overlap + chemistry distinct. 두 program 모두 FDA approval trajectory 2026-2027 expected.
3. **mexiletine off-label myotonia 1차** = Nav1.4 sodium channel block — anti-arrhythmic class IB 의 myotonia 적응증 expansion. RCT-grade evidence 2016+ (Logigian + Statland trials). 현재 DM1 myotonia symptomatic 1차.
4. **DM1 vs DM2 distinct mechanism** — DM1 = DMPK 3'UTR CTG repeat / DM2 = CNBP/ZNF9 intron 1 CCTG repeat. 양쪽 모두 toxic RNA foci + MBNL1 sequestration + CUGBP1 hyperactivation 공통 paradigm. 양자-VQE 의 RNA hairpin 모델링 fit.
5. **CDM (congenital DM1)** = maternal anticipation + ≥1000 CTG repeats + neonatal hypotonia + intellectual disability + early mortality. cross-pediatric_rare + newborn_perinatal axis 직접 fit.
6. **DM1 cardiac conduction defect** = first-degree AV block + bundle branch block + sudden cardiac death risk. ICD primary prophylaxis 가 ESC 2018 + AHA 2019 guideline recommendation. cross-cardiac_arrhythmia_extended.
7. **DM1 daytime sleepiness + central hypersomnia** = modafinil + armodafinil 1차 + pitolisant research P2/3 (cross-narcolepsy_specific 의 mechanism overlap). REM sleep dysregulation + central nervous system 직접 involve.
8. **DM systemic — endocrine + cataract + GI motility + manic mood** = single-gene multisystem 의 paradigm. cross-endocrine_thyroid_pituitary + ophthalmology + GI + mood 직접 cross-link.
9. **K-DM framework + 산정특례** — 한국 myotonic dystrophy 등록 + 산정특례 V code + 한국 임상 framework. K-pharma cross-link.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, DM1 + DM2 임상 의미 한정.

